# Cloudflare Pages headers.
# no-cache = the browser MUST revalidate before reusing a cached file, so a new deploy
# shows up on a normal refresh (returns 304 when unchanged, so it's still fast).
# This is the fix for the "I pushed but still see the old build" hard-refresh problem.
/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
